# Render Redirects for FactCheck App

# Redirect all API calls to API Gateway
/api/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/api/:splat 200
/auth/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/auth/:splat 200
/users/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/users/:splat 200
/chat/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/chat/:splat 200
/news/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/news/:splat 200
/links/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/links/:splat 200
/admin/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/admin/:splat 200
/community/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/community/:splat 200
/posts/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/posts/:splat 200
/votes/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/votes/:splat 200
/comments/* https://factcheck-api-gateway.onrender.com/comments/:splat 200

# SPA fallback - all other routes serve index.html
